            <p><button class="btn btn-primary">Find out more</button></p>

        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
            <h4 class="text-info">Researchers</h4>
            <p>Find the latest resources to advance your research. Manage data. Publish your work. Cite and be cited.</p>
            <p><button class="btn btn-primary">Find out more</button></p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
            <h4 class="text-info">Teaching Staff</h4>
            <p>Strengthen your teaching. Work with our Library experts to lift your students’ research and learning skills.</p>
            <p><button class="btn btn-primary">Find out more</button></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr />

    <div class="row mt-3">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
            <img src="~/Content/images/exhibition.jpg" class="img-fluid w-100" style="height:30vh;" />
